io.elegie.luchess.core.domain.entities

Class Game

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.elegie.luchess.core.domain.entities.Game

  • public class Game
extends java.lang.Object
    A game object. Moves are stored in a text format, for performance reasons. The class also provides an id field, so that implementations may uniquely distinguish their games, if needed.
